name: _brain/grease_
description: "Older neighbor in the street with rolllerblade brand rollerblades hit by a car and his helment wasn't buckled and his head split open. Brain all over the street and sometimes in the heat his brain grease seeps into the asphalt. One time in a puddle of brain grease we set off a whole roll of caps with a hammer and damn near deafened me into my 30s. The brain grease caught a flame and shone bright neon green for what felt like a lifetime." - Deleted 2012 facebook post by Taran Noah Smith
